==English==
===Noun===
'''sleeve''' (plural: '''sleeves''')

# the part of a [[garment]] that covers the [[arm]]
#: ''The sleeves on my [[coat]] are too long.''
# a (usually tubular) covering or lining
#: ''This [[bearing]] requires a sleeve so the [[shaft]] will fit [[snug]]ly.''

